name: Overall Health
description: Survey includes information about how participants report levels of individual health.

name: Lifestyle
description: Survey includes information on participant smoking, alcohol and recreational drug use.

name: The Basics
description: This survey includes participant demographic information.

name: Family Medical History
description: Survey includes information about the medical history of a participant’s immediate biological family members.

name: Health Care Access & Utilization
description: Survey includes information about a participant’s access to and use of health care.

name: Personal Medical History
description: This survey includes information about past medical history, including medical conditions and approximate age of diagnosis.
